    {
      "id": "E:note:row689561:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "58 year old Portugese speaking male admitted to MICU for stent    placement [**2",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row689561#s1",
      "text": "58 year old Portugese speaking male admitted to MICU for stent    placement [**2-15**] TBM with PMH OSA, afib with RVR, DM, HTN, ARF now CRI    thought initial insult d/t NSIAD use, (had HD x1 at [**Hospital3 2241**], none    since), baseline creatinine 2.5."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row689561:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt initially at [**Hospital1 959**] admitted for    paresthesias, back/sciatic n",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row689561#s2",
      "text": "Pt initially at [**Hospital1 959**] admitted for    paresthesias, back/sciatic nerve pain; intubated for airway protection    d/t altered mental status, trached/PEG after failure to wean with #7    Portex, chronic vent, also with persistent FUO and treated with    multiple abx, recurrent diarrhea, work-up negative, able to eventually    wean to PS; transferred to [**Hospital 25**] rehab where he has been for 1    month, while at [**Name (NI) 25**], pt with persistent diarrhea, so TF stopped,    then sent to CHA with fevers and hypotension; sent to CHA with    urosepsis, treated with vanco/zosyn, then only zosyn, found TBM on CT;    prior to transfer pt went into rapid afib, was treated with adenosine,    converted to flutter, rec d dilt and lopressor IV, then started on dilt    gtt, weaned off to PO dilt."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row689561:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Transfer to MICU for mgt chronically vented    pt and planned for trach stent pl",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row689561#s3",
      "text": "Transfer to MICU for mgt chronically vented    pt and planned for trach stent placement."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row689561:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Of note, patient s PEG is now    a 16fr foley catheter in abd, unable to confirm",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row689561#s4",
      "text": "Of note, patient s PEG is now    a 16fr foley catheter in abd, unable to confirm correct placement by    CXR, thus may not be safe to use; am PO dilt held, given 1x IV dose    instead."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row689561:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Events- cont on heparin for right ij thrombus at 1950u/hr ptt    therapeutic at ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row689561#s5",
      "text": "Events- cont on heparin for right ij thrombus at 1950u/hr ptt    therapeutic at 60.4. needs repeat ptt at [**2159**]."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row689561:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Hypernatremia (high sodium)    Assessment:    Na down to 144 this am.",
      "code": null,
